---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("March 23 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BaseLayout
  title="Prepare Nashville Home for Allergy Season"
  description={isPublished ? "Nashville allergy season is brutal. Prepare your home with a strategic deep clean that reduces pollen, dust & dander. Tips for Green Hills, Brentwood & beyond." : "Coming Soon: How to Prepare Your Nashville Home for Allergy Season"}
  ogImage="https://thevalleycleanteam.com/og-image.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="How to Prepare Your Nashville Home for Allergy Season"
    description="Beat Tennessee allergies before they start. Discover how to prepare your Nashville home for allergy season with strategic deep cleaning techniques."
    publishDate="March 23 2026"
    author={author}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Allergy/Health
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          How to Prepare Your Nashville Home for Allergy Season
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming March 23 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>March 23 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- DIRECT ANSWER BLOCK - Critical for AEO -->
        <div
          class="bg-[#FFA985]/10 border-l-4 border-[#FFA985] p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-lg"
        >
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium mb-0">
            <strong>Quick Answer:</strong> To prepare your Nashville home for
            allergy season, focus on minimizing allergens with thorough cleaning
            and strategic maintenance. Regular cleaning routines, air filtration,
            and allergen-proofing your living spaces can significantly reduce
            symptoms. Start with the key steps below for a healthier home
            environment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          How Can You Prepare Your Nashville Home for Allergy Season?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Beating allergy season starts with reducing the allergens that build
          up indoors. A combination of consistent cleaning habits, better air
          filtration, and a few targeted home upgrades can make a noticeable
          difference in how you feel throughout the season.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Allergens in Nashville: What to Expect
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Nashville's lush greenery makes it a vibrant place to live, but it also
          means dealing with seasonal allergens like pollen, dust mites, and
          mold. Understanding the types of allergens prevalent in the area helps
          you prepare your home effectively.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Essential Steps to Allergy-Proof Your Home
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Combat allergies head-on with these strategic measures:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>
            <strong>Regular cleaning:</strong> Implement a systematic
            <a href="/services/regular-cleaning" class="text-[#FFA985] hover:underline"
              >recurring cleaning</a
            > schedule focusing on dust-prone areas, and vacuum carpets and rugs
            using a HEPA filter vacuum cleaner.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Air filtration:</strong> Invest in high-efficiency air
            filters for your HVAC system to trap airborne particles, and consider
            portable air purifiers in high-traffic rooms.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Humidity control:</strong> Keep indoor humidity levels below
            50% to deter mold growth. Dehumidifiers can be particularly useful
            during Nashville's humid months.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Bedding and upholstery:</strong> Wash bedding weekly in hot
            water and use allergen-proof covers for pillows and mattresses to
            block dust mites.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Windows and doors:</strong> Seal any gaps and use weather
            stripping to keep pollen out, and keep windows closed during high
            pollen counts.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Specialist Cleaning: An Investment in Health
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Employing trained cleaning specialists can make a significant
          difference. At The Valley Clean Team, our veteran-owned operation in
          Nashville cleans your home with military precision. A seasonal
          <a href="/services/deep-cleaning" class="text-[#FFA985] hover:underline"
            >deep clean</a
          > is especially effective at clearing built-up allergens. Here's how our
          service stands out:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>
            <strong>Meticulous cleaning:</strong> Our specialists follow a precise
            checklist, targeting common allergen hotspots.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Veteran accountability:</strong> We guarantee results with a
            commitment to integrity and precision.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Transparent pricing:</strong> Our services start at $125, with
            no hidden fees&mdash;only clear, upfront costs.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Why Choose The Valley Clean Team?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Choosing the right cleaning service is critical to maintaining a
          healthy home. Here's why The Valley Clean Team is Nashville's preferred
          choice:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>
            <strong>Local expertise:</strong> As a Nashville-based company, we
            understand the local allergen challenges and how to tackle them
            effectively.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Community focused:</strong> We are committed to serving our
            community with the highest standards of cleanliness and care.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Proven methodologies:</strong> Our cleaning processes adhere
            to strict standard operating procedures, ensuring consistent and
            thorough results.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Book Your Allergy-Season Cleaning Today
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Don't let allergies dictate your comfort. The Valley Clean Team is
          ready to help you reclaim your home and your time. Schedule a
          guaranteed cleaning service today and experience the precision of
          veteran-owned accountability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">March 23 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )})
  <!-- Nashville Services CTA -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-[#FFA985]/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Professional Cleaning Services in Nashville, TN
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
        The Valley Clean Team serves Nashville and surrounding areas with reliable,
        thorough cleaning &mdash; including deep cleaning built for allergy season.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/locations/nashville"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-[#FFA985] text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition"
        >
          View Nashville Services
        </a>
        <a
          href="/locations/nashville/deep-cleaning/"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-[#FFA985] text-[#FFA985] font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-[#FFA985] hover:text-white transition"
        >
          Book a Deep Clean
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
